# CLAUDE.md - <REPO NAME>

Always-loaded context. Keep it SHORT and actionable: it is evaluated every turn, and
bloated context files reduce agent success and raise cost. Point at the registries;
do not inline them.

`AGENTS.md` should mirror this file (the cross-tool standard) so Codex/Gemini read the
same constitution. A pre-commit `cmp -s AGENTS.md CLAUDE.md` copy keeps them identical.

